  "title": "A fireball spotted falling into the sea by a group of fishermen in Florianópolis [2004]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/10/a-fireball-spotted-falling-into-the-sea-by-a-group-of-fishermen-in-florianopolis-2004/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-hI",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MAY 18th, 2004.</strong> Time: 8:30 am. Duration: 01 minute. An unidentified flying object was seen in front of Praia do Campeche, city of Florianópolis, State of Santa Catarina, for approximately 1 minute. According to the witness, the UFO was a &#8220;yellow fireball&#8221; was &#8220;the size of a car&#8221; and was approximately 1 km away from the observer. In addition to the witness, several fishermen also spotted the object going on a North/South trajectory and &#8220;falling into the sea near Ilha do Campeche&#8221;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.642. &#8220;O</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">corrência de objeto voador não identificado na Praia do Campeche, Florianópolis, Santa Catarina&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
